title: Mick Taylor - rench TV doc. 1998
description:
Mick Taylor - French TV
La Sur Route Avec

A 1998 French TV Bio on Mick Taylor.
One can go on and on about Mick Taylor and the
People he has played with, a Who's Who of Rock n Roll History

Mick talks about his first ever concert (Bill Hailey & the Comets)
and the Influeces on Him(Albert King, Muddy Waters) and how he became
the Guitar Player that he is today, he talks candidly of his time with
the Bluesbreakers, Rolling Stones & Bob Dylan & what he got out each Experience
